# This is a reference file to help you modify the Replit configuration
# Copy and paste these instructions to set up a workflow for the run button

# 1. Go to the Replit interface and click on "Tools" in the sidebar
# 2. Click on "Workflows"
# 3. Click "Create a workflow"
# 4. Name it "Run NTFY Script"
# 5. Use the following configuration:

# Shell command to run:
python run_ntfy.py

# This will make the run button execute our custom script with the
# pre-configured settings instead of trying to start a web server.